com.resourcemanager.controller

Class UserController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.resourcemanager.controller.UserController

  • @Controller
public class UserController
extends java.lang.Object
    This controller responds to the user input and uses the service layer to create, read, update or delete the User data model objects. This controller receives the input, optionally validates it and then passes the input to the model and directs the user back to a view to display the model and accept further user input.
